            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Hic</supplied> quiescit in pace Lupicinus <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">qu</supplied>i vixit <expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>nn</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pl</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan> LXX <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>ses</ex></expan> II et d<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>es</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>X Veneria coniux carissima titu<lb break="no" n="4"/>lum posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwischen Z. 3 und Z. 4 der Inschrift Darstellung eines Christograms mit Alpha und Omega und symmetrisch flankierenden Tauben. (B): Z. 2 men(ses) III (RICG); men(ses) II (CIL, ILCV, Gose). Z. 2-3: des / ... (RICG); de / X (CIL, ILCV, Gose).</p>
            </div>
